{"tid":335254,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"重新攜手 Zeiss 的 Nokia 8 將在 8 月 16 於英國發表","createTime":"2017-07-25T12:26:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-26T03:30:54.000Z","uid":25125,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8c268774e5b18502189760dd4a9e85d389a35efa","tid":335254,"uid":25125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T12:26:49.000Z","msg":"重新攜手 Zeiss 的 Nokia 8 將在 8 月 16 於英國發表<br />\nby Chevelle.fu   2017.07.25 05:43PM<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.cool3c.com/files/media/g/s/m/a/r/e/n/a/0/0/gsmarena_002_57.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia.cool3c.com%2Ffiles%2Fmedia%2Fg%2Fs%2Fm%2Fa%2Fr%2Fe%2Fn%2Fa%2F0%2F0%2Fgsmarena_002_57.jpg&h=9fd08833&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n根據國外媒體已經陸續收到的邀請函， HMD 旗下 Nokia 品牌的高階機 Nokia 8 將選在 8 月 16 日於英國倫敦發表； Nokia 8 據稱將搭載 5.3吋的 QHD顯示器，基於高通 Snapdragon 835處理器，搭配 4GB或是 6GB RAM ，內建 64GB 儲存與雙 SIM 卡，最大的特色是將搭載與 Carl Zeiss 合作的雙 13MP 鏡頭，據稱提供銅、藍與銀色三種顏色。<br />\n<br />\n新聞來源： The Verge<br />\n<br />\n轉貼自: <a href=\"https://www.cool3c.com/article/127058\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cool3c.com%2Farticle%2F127058&d=ammElTl8ef0XgIZwl6iYv%2F%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=225203de\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cool3c.com/article/127058</a><br />\n癮科技facebook: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cool3c.tw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcool3c.tw&d=ammElTl8ef0XgIZwl6iYv%2F%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=4904c40b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cool3c.tw</a>"},{"pid":"b68b33f375ec501bff5f698a79951293781cd236","tid":335254,"uid":55951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T14:15:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>重新攜手 Zeiss 的 Nokia 8 將在 8 月 16 於英國發表<br />\nby Chevelle.fu   2017.07.25 05:43PM<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://media.cool3c.com/files/media/g/s/m/a/r/e/n/a/0/0/gsmarena_002_57.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia